Title: One to Go (2)
Plot: The CSI team is shocked and saddened when, after working with Dr. Raymond Langston on the 'Dick & Jane' murders, Grissom announces that his time as a CSI has come to an end and offers Langston a permanent position on the CSI team.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Laurence Fishburne, David Berman, Liz Vassey, Jimmi Simpson, Katheryn Winnick, Matt O'Leary, Mark Rolston, Wynn Everett, Marc Vann, Archie Kao, Sheeri Rappaport, Jon Wellner, Larry Sullivan, Bill Irwin, Josh Jacobs
